Vice President Yemi Osinbajo on behalf of the President, Major General Muhammadu Buhari (retd.), on Wednesday, unveiled the PMB Ministerial Scorecard Portal and Compendium at the State House Banquet Centre, Abuja. Present at the unveiling were the Minister of Information and Culture, Lai Mohammed; Minister of Industry, Trade and Investment, Niyi Adebayo; Women affairs minister, Pauline Tallen; and Minister of Youths and Sports, Sunday Dare, among others. See the pictures below (Credit: Tolani Alli): 